items.name: ATmega328P-Development-Board-with-USB-C
items.description: This repository contains the KiCad project files and PCB design for an ATmega328P-based development board , featuring a USB-C connector for programming and power. The design integrates power regulation, USB-to-serial interface, ISP headers, and additional circuitry to make prototyping with the ATmega328P simple and reliable.
